<dict>
    <!-- Phase 6 plan 01 — microphone TCC prompt text.
         macOS shows this string in the permission dialog when the user
         selects a non-null audio device for the first time. Keep honest:
         StoryCapture only opens the mic when the user enables it per
         recording (D-02 non-sticky opt-in). -->
